{"tid":805930,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解呢個世界有咁多人鍾意政治政確？？“","createTime":"2018-09-04T09:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T10:49:19.000Z","uid":187227,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"263ca4a8819ba843328334f312e2088464f1a2b4","tid":805930,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n以海難沉船為例<br />\n係未知救生艇足唔足夠嘅情況下<br />\n都一定會比老弱婦孺上船先<br />\n咁當然 比大肚婆，小朋友，女人上船先好合理<br />\n但係點解會比老人家上船先？首先佢哋對社會生產力最低，其次佢哋都一把年紀好話唔好聽都就快釘。如果以青年同中年男人嘅生命作為賭注嚟救呢班老人 其實算唔算好傻？<br />\n當然會有人話男人們殿後係因為佢哋身體強壯 生存機率高 但係所謂欺山莫欺水 可能都係高得7-8%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實上面嘅只係例子，我真正想講嘅係點解無論東西方國家都咁鍾意政治政確 明明呢樣野只會拖累發展 又無任何現實幫助 好多時喺政治政確只會衍生出更多犧牲者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31766251b96b3578b5fb7e514ed1ac3fbff24c60","tid":805930,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cded85d49768bcc31aeb38a32eb6e901d390c65","tid":805930,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7c6ea36645569e5f2ac3847790a07365e5d41b0","tid":805930,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6829853d22da3a750223edfee64bfa7935c3f5d","tid":805930,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cded85d49768bcc31aeb38a32eb6e901d390c65","tid":805930,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:22:31.000Z","msg":"點解大笨象打丈要辣椒醬？？<br />\n呢個世界好多嘢係無得解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a378c9d2b5b