:65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"如果判斷情形係可以控制局面的，咁會選擇政治正確的方法。<br />\n<br />\n如果火燒眼眉，就會自私求生，因為求生慾。<br />\n<br />\n所以答案係 判斷情形有幾緊急，你可以話人係偽善，但我會話道德都係有層次嘅。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:16:04.000Z","msg":"我當然明白人係要帶著面具<br />\n但係喺政治政確下衍生嘅犧牲者只會更多<br />\n<br />\n以之前嘅唐氏綜合症選美冠軍為例<br />\n莫非咁樣真係對其他參賽者公平？"},{"pid":"2ce3392f06fc48a7656007a90e933c68ea56ddd9","tid":805930,"uid":206083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:16:49.000Z","msg":"你做出黎既，永遠比你認知既道德標準低幾級<br />\n人無完人，但條底線點set睇既就係你個天花點set"},{"pid":"0615d4af756805a8d7d6456e6f86c3092f5086e5","tid":805930,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ce3392f06fc48a7656007a90e933c68ea56ddd9","tid":805930,"uid":206083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:16:49.000Z","msg":"你做出黎既，永遠比你認知既道德標準低幾級<br />\n人無完人，但條底線點set睇既就係你個天花點set"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"人當然要活喺道德之下<br />\n因為一個社會一個文明都係要靠道德嚟鞏固<br />\n<br />\n所以君子先咁值得讚賞 因為佢哋可以執行大義<br />\n<br />\n但係我認為政治政確只係有一群人唔敢面對醜惡嘅自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a70002183705d7d022512e0a43adfce6d73deb","tid":805930,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2393a8c258ae9f573c5411312164856d695e4774","tid":805930,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class